snippet: Stocks moved ahead, passing multiyear highs as traders awaited President Obama’s State of the Union address.
abstract: Dow Jones industrial average rises above 14,000 to its highest close of the year, putting it within 1 percent of its own record.
lead_paragraph: Stocks moved ahead, passing multiyear highs as traders awaited President Obama’s State of the Union address.

headline.main: Dow Ends Above 14,000 for Year’s Highest Close
